originalText.text:
When my in-laws  decided to sell their apartment they asked me to contact Eugenia. The reason is that she had sold their first apartment in Riverdale. When I contacted her on behalf of my in-laws. She
did not hesitate to accept the Offer to sell their apartment.       My in-laws English is limited and Eugenia' s Spanish is limited. My in-laws had relocated to another state. We are all very happy with the successful sale and the customer  service and professional service that Eugenia  , the owner of Foxworth Realty offers.  Ben Ovelar and the family.

originalText.text:
I was apartment hunting in NYC this summer and reached out to 20+ different real estate offices and brokers... Foxworth Realty was one of the only companies that gave me the time of day. Eugenia and Adulis listened to what I needed, presented me with various options, and took time to SHOW UP and show me units that fit my criteria while other companies were no-shows.
Anyone who needs a reliable and honest representative in NYC's notoriously difficult housing/ rental market should direct their business to Foxworth Realty.
